#29004
Mistif's Office~
BEHOLD! The office of the dark and mysterious Mistif.
As you enter the room you get the feeling that someone is watching you.
   To your left is a computer. And to your right is a bookshelf filled 
with volume after volume of books from programming to fantasy adventure. 
   Directly accross the room is a large picture window overlooking
the steep cliffs this office was build into. Dark blue draperies border 
the window. There is a lavish love seat setting in front of it. 
~
